text.section:
"Health care facility" means:
A hospital as defined in § 19-301 of this title;
A health maintenance organization as defined in § 19-701(g) of this title;
A freestanding ambulatory care facility as defined in § 19-3B-01 of this title;
An assisted living facility as defined in § 19-1801 of this title;
A laboratory as defined in § 17-201 of this article;
A home health agency as defined in § 19-401 of this title;
A residential treatment center as defined in § 19-301 of this title;
A comprehensive rehabilitation facility as defined in § 19-1201 of this title; and
A forensic laboratory as defined in § 17-2A-01 of this article.
